    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/a7ad4c52f5e7e2b3fccd63230b684afb.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Tile Town!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy this simple (but challenging) medieval-themed strategy game played on a hexagonal grid. Plop down various building tiles, each with its own preferred neighboring tiles, to get the highest score possible. Find the best placement for each tile and make use of special perfect placement bonuses. Hit the next score threshold to gain additional batches before you run out of tiles. Unlock new types of tiles, new levels, improve your high scores and compare them to other players on the Steam leaderboards, or go for a stroll in the first person mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/b7fade46f8e67804f7e190b9babfa3b3.poster.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/b7fade46f8e67804f7e190b9babfa3b3.webm?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/b7fade46f8e67804f7e190b9babfa3b3.mp4?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/d3f75b9487b0fa647f6c2b346cdb6582.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tile Town offers the following features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 different levels</strong> and a special <strong>procedurally generated island</strong> guarantee replayability </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30+ various tiles</strong> with adorable custom-made buildings and props, each with randomized appearance </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vibrant and picturesque</strong> medieval-themed visuals </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First person camera view</strong> for walking around your town together with other peasants </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Depth of field</strong> option to make the town looks extra tiny and adorable </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Peaceful and relaxing soundtrack</strong> to complete the atmosphere </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>14 Steam achievements</strong> to unlock </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam leaderboards</strong> for comparing your scores to other players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key rebinding</strong> and a partial controller support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 languages</strong> (at the moment) including English, French, Czech, German, Chinese, Spanish</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/9807ce240fc27c7608056f742c0d5b85.poster.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/9807ce240fc27c7608056f742c0d5b85.webm?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/9807ce240fc27c7608056f742c0d5b85.mp4?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Tile Town <strong>doesn't</strong> have and will not have: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4X strategy mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/4cf2ecec81159afed8907bf0f90d0795.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Found a bug? Got feedback or suggestions?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tile Town started in Early access and got to the current state thanks to the support, feedback and suggestions from players. Whether you want to leave a feedback, give a suggestion or report a bug, head over to the Community discussions and your voice will be heard. Thank you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/e16d13b37277b6d1c6b53eaf05cdbd28.poster.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/e16d13b37277b6d1c6b53eaf05cdbd28.webm?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/e16d13b37277b6d1c6b53eaf05cdbd28.mp4?t=1740268934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164780/extras/c5c70997e247e38286df313a16a94ccb.avif?t=1740268934\" width=640 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional information</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tile Town was made with love by a small indie developer One Goose Army, with passion for simple, fun and chill games. The game was inspired by other amazing titles such as Dorfromantik and Islanders.</p>",
